PART I
ITEM 1. BUSINESS
Our Strategy
We grow , diversify and build our business throug h a combination of organic and inorganic strategic initiatives. Our ability to grow our
business is influenced by:
•personal consumption expenditure (“PCE”) growth
•driving cash and check transactions toward electronic forms of payment
•increasing our share in the payments space
Growing our business also includes supplementing our core network by providing integrated value-added products and services and
enhanced payment capabilities to capture new payment flows, such as business to business (“B2B”), person to person (“P2P”),
business to consumer (“B2C”) and government payments.
 
